etischen Sprache demonstriert.  aInsights cannot only be gained through science; truth is actually revealed through the fine arts. Therefore scientists also have to be active poets.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArt and technology. 0aKnowledge, Theory of. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aIdeengeschichte. 4aKultur. 4aKunst. 4aScience and Technology Studies. 4aTechnik. 4aTechnikgeschichte. 4aWissenschaft. 4aWissenschaftsgeschichte. 4aÄsthetik. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh  aAesthetics.  aArt.  aCulture.  aHistory of Ideas.  aHistory of Science.  aHistory of Technology.  aHistory.  aScience.  aTechnology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2017z9783110547764oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839441237zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839441237423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839441237/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017